            "description": "# **Bug description:**\n\nSending empte strings in fields \"checkin\" and \"checkout\" via PATCH method that includes object:\n\n### _Payload sent_\n\n`\"bookingdates\":{\"checkin\":\"\",\"checkout\":\"\"}`\n\n### _Expected result_\n\nExpect server to return status code 400 - Bad request.\n\n### _Actual result_\n\nHowever, server returns _200 OK_ and saves corrupt data with NaNs:  \n`\"bookingdates\": { \"checkin\": \"0NaN-aN-aN\", \"checkout\": \"0NaN-aN-aN\" }`"
